## Approach

The terrestrial RLE assessment follows the IUCN RLE 2.0 in an approach described by Skowno & Monyeki, 2021[@skowno2021], using additional input data to assess a wider range of criteria. New land cover data, invasive alien plant data and ecosystem condition data from two additional regions were employed[@bell2021; @kirsten2023; @rebelo; @kotzé2025; @cogill; @skosana].

